body_html:
I tracked down the issue. The difference between builds is the automatic download version gets https://storage.googleapis.com/download.tensorflow.org/models/mobile_multibox_v1a.zip while the instructions at https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/tree/master/tensorflow/examples/android specify to download https://storage.googleapis.com/download.tensorflow.org/models/mobile_multibox_v1.zip . (notice the "a" in the file name).

One file contains multibox_location_priors.pb while the other has multibox_location_priors.txt.
